      <abstract id="aspace_281ca7f93baa5dc77b4bb8025c9d8927">The Piedmont Tuberculosis Sanatorium
        (Burkeville, Virginia) Collection includes materials from 1926-1971. The collection contains
        information relating to the operation of the sanatorium from 1918-1965. The collection
        contains administrative papers, published works of doctors, ephemera, and images.
      </abstract>
